front.title: •Tedn Dahai
front.gametext: For each other musician at same site, during any control phase you may use 1 Force to choose one opponent's alien present. That alien cannot utilize its game text for remainder of that turn.
front.lore: Male Bith musician. Member in good standing of the Intergalactic Federation of Musicians. Plays the Fanfar in Figrin D'an's band. Once worked for the Empire as a scout.

pulledBy: Soth Petikkin (when at a Jabba's Palace site you control)
